   - **`src/_components/home-divider.webc`** — Randomized animated SVG stroke divider
     - Generates random bent strokes filling available width
     - Auto-redraws every 1000ms, redraws on resize (debounced 150ms)
     - Uses feTurbulence + feDisplacementMap SVG filter with random seed per draw
     - Uses `<script webc:keep>` (inline, only on pages that include the component)
